abstract: The marriage of Miss Amy Louise Osler, daughter of Mrs. Henry Sonenblick of New York and the late David Osler, to Alexander Edward Sharp 2d took place yesterday. The bridegroom is the son of Dr. and Mrs. A.E. Sharp of San Antonio, Tex., formerly of StamFord, Conn.
headline_main: Amy Osler Is Wed To A.E. Sharp 2d
headline_print_headline: Amy Osler Is Wed To A.E. Sharp 2d
